➜湖北诗人木子/星连（广东）：无题
http://www.sohu.com/a/415324134_100115135	22082
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200828/f33e352cd64e44ac91def61887c2b4a8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝/无题（步韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/木子</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">笺中诗写意，展卷月辉台。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">和韵三千阕，挥毫引客来。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200828/cf33b8271a6144fab5cf3bbfc9a4395c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.无题（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">心留溪涧水，月落故乡台。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">缘借三千梦，茶香唤客来。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2020.7.28</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200828/119153694bd240f1b2c632a4d5153ac9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
